[SIZE="4"][b][color=#1a73e8]What is this?[/color][/b][/SIZE]
[SIZE="3"]LegionOS is an AOSP based ROM

Our mission is to offer the maximum possible stability and security, along with essential and useful features for the proper functioning of the device

Based on Android 11
[/SIZE]

[SIZE="4"][b][color=#1a73e8]Whats working?[/color][/b][/SIZE]
[SIZE="3"]Wi-Fi
RIL
Mobile data
GPS
Camera
Flashlight
Camcorder
Bluetooth
FM radio
Fingerprint reader
Face unlock
NFC
Lights
Sound/vibration[/SIZE]

[SIZE="4"][B][color="#ff0000"]CLEAN FLASH : [/COLOR][/B][/SIZE]
[SIZE="4"]Download the latest build and GApps (optional)
Reboot to recovery 
Make nandroid backup ( optional)
Wipe System, Data, Cache, Dalvik
Flash the latest build and GApps(on non Gapps build if needed)
Reboot to slot A (B if on A | A if on B) {ONLY FOR A/B PARTITION DEVICES}
Reboot[/SIZE]

[SIZE="4"][B][color="#ff0000"]DIRTY FLASH : [/COLOR][/B][/SIZE]
[SIZE="4"]Download the latest build (gapps or non Gapps)
Reboot to recovery
Flash the latest build
Change Slot {ONLY FOR A/B PARTITION DEVICES}
Wipe Cache
Reboot[/SIZE]

Note: GApps only has to be flashed once and on non gapps buildwhereas Magisk/Su is to be flashed every time you Dirty Flash the OTA Update.

